text: Voyager is a progressive metal band formed in 1999 in Perth, Western Australia. They have released 8 albums. In 2023, they represented Australia at the Eurovision Song Contest 2023 with the song "Promise", which finished in 9th place. == Sources == Category:1999 establishments in Australia Category:1990s Australian music groups Category:2000s Australian music groups Category:2010s Australian music groups Category:2020s music groups Category:Australian rock bands Category:Eurovision Song Contest entrants Category:Musical groups established in 1999 Category:Perth, Western Australia Category:Progressive metal bands
